show.description:
When Lydia, a brilliant Harvard graduate, returns to New York for an internship, she uncovers a chilling secret her enigmatic stepbrother Noah is a vampire and the powerful head of the Sinclair wine empire.
As a dangerous attraction sparks between them, Noah must wrestle with the darkness within and the taboo of their growing connection. Meanwhile, the rival Moriaty family plots the Sinclairs' downfall, threatening to expose centuries of secrets.In a world of bloodlines, betrayal, and forbidden desire, love comes with a price and survival isn’t guaranteed.
